{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I made my way back to my sister, who was not speaking to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I couldn't explain.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She was so much of a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I couldn't explain anything to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we left the wagon very, very angry with each other, with the words of my mother ringing in my ears that I had to be the big one and look after her, whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I literally held her hand in a vice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "She was forever trying to break free from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We stood in line-- it was dark-- for a long, long time, and there were very strong overhead lights.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't recall-- yes, I do recall the gates of Auschwitz because there was music playing, and I saw the band playing, and I couldn't quite work it out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They all looked like stone statues, but they were actually making music.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I see the sign, 'work is to free you.' And I was reassured, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I went in with my sister, and held and clutched, and she was practically biting to get free from me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And then, before we could realize what was happening, we were standing right in front of a most stunning-looking man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I was aware by then of males.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I've never seen a man as beautiful-- I don't remember-- with several huge Alsatians around him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the by-now popular vision of him with the pointer that he used.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he was pointing in my direction and telling me to go right, and pointing to my sister to go left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I just stood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And he again did that with a very gentle look on his face.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I didn't move without my sister, and she was really wrenching, breaking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I could-- can't tell you what physical strength was required.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
